project.name: VATSIM UK
project.description:
We are the UK division of VATSIM.net, a global community of over 100,000 aviation ethusiasts that come together to share a passion for flight simulation.

The software that our small voluntary team produces helps power the systems that support UK members - nearly 20,000 people.

All of our services are provided totally free of charge and allow our members to connect together.
